channel.title: Invalid Waypoint in Walking Queue? WILL REP
channel.description: Ok so when I'm on my server I can play just fine as long as I want... but when I log out and try to log back in... it says error connecting to server and it says invalid waypoint in walking queue, no matter where i am. I don't understand. It only happens to me. I'm the host and coder. Anyone have any ideas?
